t of modern humans was shared with Neandertals | journal = Curr. Biol. | volume = 17 | issue = 21 | pages = 1908–12 | pmid = 17949978 | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2007.10.008 | url =  | laysummary = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/19/science/19speech-web.html?ref=world | laysource = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]] | laydate = 2007-10-19 | date = November 2007 | access-date = 2010-02-02 | archive-date = 2013-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510162533/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/19/science/19speech-web.html?ref=world | dead-url = no }}</ref>这意味着人属的祖先也拥有同样的FOXP2基因。
